data.description: This beautiful contemporary move-in ready home is perfect for a First-time homebuyer or savvy investor. This home is filled with features that boast style and comfort such as a semi open kitchen making this space great for entertaining, wood cabinetry, hardwood flooring and a cozy fireplace in the great room. The area of the home provides convenient access to a range of amenities including Stonecrest Mall, Stone Mountain Park, several dining options, parks, and other things to explore in Lithonia.
